{"tid":2071882,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聯合國人權理事會譴責美國種族歧視及警暴 但未有言及調查 人權組織批評美國施壓 欺凌其他國家","createTime":"2020-06-20T07:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T08:44:45.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c233a3839789062d6fc397ac0a7348e6a17e17c8","tid":2071882,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:36:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20200620/s00014/1592590678967/%E8%81%AF%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%AA%E4%BF%83%E6%9F%A5%E7%BE%8E%E7%A8%AE%E6%97%8F%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96-%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E6%89%B9%E8%8F%AF%E5%BA%9C%E6%96%BD%E5%A3%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20200620%2Fs00014%2F1592590678967%2F%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%259F%25A5%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E6%2597%258F%25E6%25AD%25A7%25E8%25A6%2596-%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594%25E6%2589%25B9%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2596%25BD%25E5%25A3%2593&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w8ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=95145e7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20200620%2Fs00014%2F1592590678967%2F%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%259F%25A5%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E6%2597%258F%25E6%25AD%25A7%25E8%25A6%2596-%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594%25E6%2589%25B9%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2596%25BD%25E5%25A3%2593&h=37c98c7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20200620/s00014/1592590678967/%E8%81%AF%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%AA%E4%BF%83%E6%9F%A5%E7%BE%8E%E7%A8%AE%E6%97%8F%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96-%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E6%89%B9%E8%8F%AF%E5%BA%9C%E6%96%BD%E5%A3%93</a><br />\n【明報專訊】聯合國人權理事會昨一致通過決議，譴責導致美國黑人弗洛伊德死亡的種族歧視及警察暴力，但在多方閉門拉鋸下，未有點名要求調查美國的「系統性種族歧視」，而只是要求聯合國人權事務高級專員巴切萊特（Michelle Bachelet）一年內就非洲裔所受的「系統性種族歧視」提交報告。人權組織批評，已退出理事會的美國幕後施壓。<br />\n<br />\n淡化措辭 删國際調查不提美國<br />\n54個非洲國家因應美國警察涉嫌濫用暴力害死黑人弗洛伊德，向聯合國人權理事會提交了決議草案，原促請呼籲成立獨立國際委員會，作出最高層次的獨立調查，將肇事者繩之以法。當地時間周五（19日）下午表決草案前，當中措辭強烈內容一再被淡化，最初删掉「呼籲國際調查」，到了周五中午已不再提美國。最新版本是，敦請巴切萊特「準備一份關於系統性種族主義，執法機關針對非洲人、非洲裔的違反國際人權法的報告」，該報告須特別關注「弗洛伊德、其他非洲人與非裔人士之死衍生的那些事故，問責與賠償受害者」。<br />\n<br />\n美國公民自由聯盟（ACLU）人權主任達克瓦爾批評美國藉着欺凌別國，淡化決議案的歷史性，使之免受國際調查，再一次背棄了警暴犧牲者與黑人。國際人權組織「人權觀察」日內瓦分部主任費希爾（John Fisher）警告，這樣做使決議案變得含糊無意義。<br />\n<br />\n（法新社/路透社）"},{"pid":"a5988ff7981d6fb43db9de6111e381c1bd81aac4","tid":2071882,"uid":345137,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:38:50.000Z","msg":"聯合國人權理事會=支那口交支部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef219b06a779bf6ec6bc4244f492a31406793ea6","tid":2071882,"uid":100155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:40:17.000Z","msg":"How about concentration camps in China??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb824aa7aadbda5af4461d1f34592e7d18cd60b","tid":2071882,"uid":9013,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:48:43.000Z","msg":"講完出黎好似自打嘴巴咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又人權又警暴，但唔提香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b7d28eec9bebfbd46eeb56c41125dfe95a0bb2","tid":2071882,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7fb824aa7aadbda5af4461d1f34592e7d18cd60b","tid":2071882,"uid":9013,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:48:43.000Z","msg":"講完出黎好似自打嘴巴咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又人權又警暴，但唔提香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:49:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6CBAPxg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6CBAPxg.png&h=98afefc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OZKnuxh.png\" d